        "2. Essential Shopping Phrases:",
        "   - Je cherche... (I am looking for...)",
        "   - Vous avez...? (Do you have...?)",
        "   - C'est combien? (How much is it?)",
        "   - C'est trop cher. (It is too expensive.)",
        "   - Je le/la prends. (I'll take it.)",
        "   - Vous faites des réductions? (Do you give discounts?)",
        "   - Je paie par carte / en espèces. (I pay by card / in cash.)",
